    <p class="kwd-updated-line"><strong>Updated: 19 March 2026</strong> &bull; Author: <a href="/about-us/">Charlie Chao</a>, Kiwi Web Design</p>

    <p class="kwd-snippet">Most small NZ business websites cost <strong>$1,000–$6,000</strong>; eCommerce <strong>$5,000–$15,000+</strong>; custom builds <strong>$10,000–$50,000+</strong>. Hosting, content, and <strong>15% GST</strong> add to the total.</p>

